snippet.title: LemauDev
snippet.description:
Lemau Dev Chanel is dedicated for making Tutorial video , Construct 2 Tutorial , Photoshop Tutorial , Game Assets Tutorial , Unity3D tutorial and all about Game Making or Game Development tutorial which Specially with indonesia Language , nice to meet you and also im trying to make some video with english dub and try to tell you about all my knowledge about game making and game development

this time im focusing on Construct 2 tutorial indonesia or Tutorial Construct 2 for Free , Feel Free to comment and request tutorial on every each my video , i will be thanksfull if you are watching my video . hope this channel help you out and dont forget to subscribe , share and like .... cheers hi hiyu...!!

Muhammad Taufik
Lemau Dev
